      "text": "Application of ORS 450.005 to 450.245 to districts organized under former laws; savings clause. (1) Sanitary districts organized under chapter 385, Oregon Laws 1935, which were exercising the functions of sanitary districts on July 16, 1949, are vested with all rights, powers and obligations prescribed in ORS 450.005 to",
